>>> Ob01.format
AttributeError
- Static types do not have a format property, only scheme and encoding

>>> Ob01.scheme
'Ob01'
- Should be 'ob01' (lowercase) (same for Ob)

>>> Ob01.encoding
'Base32Crockford'
- Should be 'c32' (same for Ob)

>>> Ob.format
<function Ob.format()>
- Should be a property

